  "subject": "Use jdk 11.0.11_9 in docker images",
  "commit_message": "Use jdk 11.0.11_9 in docker images\n\nThe onap java image only supports the java jre, but some of the\npolicy components need the java jdk.  Unfortunately, using alpine\n\"apk\" to install openjdk11 does not result in the latest java jdk\nversion.\n\nCopied the onap-jre Dockerfile contents and modified it to specify\nthe adopt jdk instead of the adopt jre.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-3486\nChange-Id: Icf833f1b1a068842d2141a84b5b3fe9aa1017b80\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
